OL,5, Durham University's biggest donor has  
OL,6, withdrawn his financial support over   
OL,7, what he described as "ridiculous and   
OL,8, ineffective" Covid-19 restrictions.    
OL,10,FMark Hillery, who donated #7m between  
OL,11,F2015 and 2021, said students were being
OL,12,Fleft as the "final members of society" 
OL,13,Fto be subjected to the rules.          
OL,15,FHe also hit out at January's temporary 
OL,16,Freintroduction of online teaching.     
OL,18,FThe university said it appreciated his 
OL,19,Fsupport and added that health, safety  
OL,20,Fand wellbeing were a priority.         
